{"body": "Upper Mattaponi Tribal Code of Law. 103 Purpose The purpose of this First Election Law is to provide guidance under the law for the Election Commission to call and conduct the First Election in October 2023 in accordance with the requirements of the Constitution of the Tribe. ( Res. No. 2023-005 \u00a7 1.2(1) .)", "num": "103", "path": "library|Upper Mattaponi Tribal Code of Law|48|1|1.2(1)", "title": "103 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/umitribe/council/code/\u00a748-103"}
